## Promotion Rule

No backlog item becomes a product claim until it has:

- a source capture or official source URL rechecked in the current session
- a scoped problem statement
- a falsifier or proof obligation
- a runnable packet, source-body review, or blocked receipt
- a Crucible verdict or explicit `UNVERIFIABLE`
- a do-not-claim boundary

